    {
      "name": "DriftWithdrawalTicket",
      "docs": [
        "Per-user withdrawal ticket for the two-phase unstake flow.",
        "",
        "Phase 1 (`withdraw`): creates this ticket, locks the shares.",
        "Phase 2 (`settle_withdrawal`): after `unlock_ts`, executes the CPI and returns underlying."
      ],
      "type": {
        "kind": "struct",
        "fields": [
          {
            "name": "position",
            "docs": [
              "The AdapterPosition this ticket belongs to."
            ],
            "type": "pubkey"
          },
          {
            "name": "shares",
            "docs": [
              "Shares being withdrawn (locked from the position)."
            ],
            "type": "u64"
          },
          {
            "name": "min_amount_out",
            "docs": [
              "Minimum acceptable underlying out (slippage protection)."
            ],
            "type": "u64"
          },
          {
            "name": "unlock_ts",
            "docs": [
              "Unix timestamp when the cooldown expires and settlement is allowed."
            ],
            "type": "i64"
          },
          {
            "name": "is_settled",
            "docs": [
              "Whether this ticket has been settled."
            ],
            "type": "bool"
          },
          {
            "name": "created_ts",
            "docs": [
              "Unix timestamp when the ticket was created."
            ],
            "type": "i64"
          },
          {
            "name": "bump",
            "docs": [
              "PDA bump."
            ],
            "type": "u8"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "VaultStatus",
      "docs": [
        "Operational status of an adapter vault.",
        "",
        "- `Active` — deposits and withdrawals are allowed.",
        "- `DepositsPaused` — deposits blocked, withdrawals still allowed.",
        "- `Paused` — deposits and withdrawals are blocked; config remains intact.",
        "- `Deprecated` — vault is permanently retired; no operations allowed.",
        "",
        "# Serialization order",
        "`DepositsPaused` is appended **after** `Deprecated` so that the Borsh",
        "discriminants of the original three variants (`Active` = 0, `Paused` = 1,",
        "`Deprecated` = 2) remain unchanged — preserving backward compatibility",
        "with all existing on-chain vault accounts."
      ],
      "repr": {
        "kind": "rust"
      },
      "type": {
        "kind": "enum",
        "variants": [
          {
            "name": "Active"
          },
          {
            "name": "Paused"
          },
          {
            "name": "Deprecated"
          },
          {
            "name": "DepositsPaused"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
